text: Barrel Rock is a small barren rock within the edge of Cohasset Harbor in Cohasset, Massachusetts, USA. The rock is north of Sutton Rocks, northwest of Quarry Point, south of Chittenden Rock, and east of Brush Island. It is located at ==See also== *Green Island (Massachusetts) *Great Brewster *Little Brewster *Middle Brewster *Outer Brewster *Long Island *Tewksbury Rock (Massachusetts) *Martin Ledge (Massachusetts) Category:Coastal islands of Massachusetts Category:Islands of Norfolk County, Massachusetts
